title: Feeling Guilty for Feeding Your Kids Crap
itunes:title: Feeling Guilty for Feeding Your Kids Crap
description:
Get the Free Course here:
https://phit.click/freecourse

 

In this episode we help you let go of the guilt for teaching your kids to eat crap. So many of us get caught up in worry about our kids' nutrition and what they eat that we totally forget that change must start with us.

In this episode you leave feeling ready to make your changes and have some practical strategies of what to do for your kids, too.
